      "versionNonce": 1174,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "RECONCILIATION SWEEP\n(Temporal workflow or cron, every 15\u201330 min)\n1. Query claims: status=claimed AND created_at > 1hr old\n2. RAZORPAY API CALL (read-only): GET /v1/payments/:id\n   (Payment.Fetch) \u2014 returns authoritative status:\n   authorized | captured | failed\n3. Resolve claim to succeeded/failed accordingly,\n   update invoice payment status, release lingering lock",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "r86",
      "originalText": "RECONCILIATION SWEEP\n(Temporal workflow or cron, every 15\u201330 min)\n1. Query claims: status=claimed AND created_at > 1hr old\n2. RAZORPAY API CALL (read-only): GET /v1/payments/:id\n   (Payment.Fetch) \u2014 returns authoritative status:\n   authorized | captured | failed\n3. Resolve claim to succeeded/failed accordingly,\n   update invoice payment status, release lingering lock",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 14
    },
